{"tid":2383344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"酒店親子Staycation｜5歲起飛訓練小機師！Ritz-Carlton 106樓跟專業飛行教官玩一小時模擬飛行","createTime":"2021-01-28T00:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T01:33:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1c44ea9ebd8e91fd041e9dceb63caedcbdc9edc4","tid":2383344,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T00:08:50.000Z","msg":"疫下酒店staycation又有新搞作，今次記者來到全港最高酒店──香港麗思卡爾頓酒店（The Ritz-Carlton）106樓的房間，跟飛行教官學習駕駛飛機，在430米高、180度景致下體驗模擬飛行。<br />\n<br />\nJunior Aviator Academy （JAA）是由航空業管理層、資深機長及民航處認可的飛行安全教官組成的飛行訓練團隊，提供專業航空培訓，並希望通過基礎航空知識，教授STEM（Science, Technology, Engineering &amp; Mathematics）教育學習活動模式，幫助學生確定飛行夢想、提升英語聽說能力、自信心、分析力、危機應變和學習意願。今次JAA飛行訓練團隊來到香港麗思卡爾頓酒店的106樓，把酒店房間改裝成模擬駕駛艙，讓小朋友staycation時也可以揸飛機。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210128/4PS6MCRLURBADIETQV3FAFSXA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210128%2F4PS6MCRLURBADIETQV3FAFSXA4%2F&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cUzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=d8635aae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210128%2F4PS6MCRLURBADIETQV3FAFSXA4%2F&h=836d8744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210128/4PS6MCRLURBADIETQV3FAFSXA4/</a>"},{"pid":"ca728405cb90dd0081145133356f6ce32e00a6cd","tid":2383344,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T00:10:01.000Z","msg":"rich"},{"pid":"fdf54ed96bfa6c5ed4f0e05496fb75e8ea1dfd39","tid":2383344,"uid":361751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T00:10:50.000Z","msg":"幫助學生確定飛行夢想、提升<span class=\"red\">英語</span>聽說能力、自信心、分析力、危機應變和學習意願<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n練好普通話先啦<br />\n第時入集中營都識叫肚餓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5189ac54bbb0f38